                  <li class="program-course">
            <a href="/study/2014-2015/courses/edes-365" class="program-course-title">
              EDES 365 Experiences in Communications (3 credits)              <!---->            </a>
            <div class="program-course-description">
              <div class="program-course-description-inner">
                <div id="node-23392" class=" clearfix">
  
  
  
  <div class="meta">
    <p>Offered by: Integrated Studies in Ed (<a href="/study/2014-2015/node/608">Faculty of Education</a>)</p>
      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Secondary Education              : Personal development of students as communicators; involvement of the imagination in individual and group projects in language and in another chosen medium of communication: analysis of experiences in projects in relation to general problems of communication.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              This course is not scheduled for the 2014-2015 academic year.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-instructors">
